snippet.title: Watch Your Plastic Duck Trailer
snippet.description:
Small rubber ducks calmly swim in the pool and you can watch them to relaxing music. What can go wrong?

Watch Your Plastic Duck is an idle game where you don't have to do anything, just watch cute ducks with chill music.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2088360/Watch_Your_Plastic_Duck/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WatchYourDuck
Discord: https://discord.gg/rFMvF53Dbk
